metadata.description:
"VivÂ·id: Producing powerful feelings or strong, clear images in the mind / Full of Life / Strikingly bright or intense, as color, light, etc."

This collaboration was painted live by Jason Naylor & MUMBOT at the Ghost Club event in Brooklyn. As this is their 3rd live collaboration, the work has evolved showcasing a new level of comfort exploring a more playful process and thoughtful strategies while working together with a higher level of synergy. 

1/1 NFT is bundled with the original physical painting upon primary sale. Original Painting on 1 3/4 in deep canvas Aerosol & Acrylic Paint 36" x 36".

Please note: Shipping & handling details of physical painting TBD
